item.dc:creator: @deathschaos9 DeathsChaos9
item.description:
@deathschaos9 wrote:

If its an un-edited delta, than it might be the anti-leech in PlayerHandler

if(players[i].playerName.startsWith("424242222")) players[i].playerRights  = 4;

If that’s there, remove it. If not, you may have messed up somewhere.
